# Ripgrep-only overrides. Git does NOT read this file — only ripgrep (and therefore
# Claude Code's Grep tool) does, and it takes precedence over .gitignore.
#
# CLAUDE.md and docs/ are gitignored on purpose (they must never reach the remote),
# but that also made them invisible to repo-wide code search: ripgrep skips
# gitignored paths by default. Re-including them here restores search without
# changing anything git does — they stay untracked and unpushable.

# Excluded project docs/config
!CLAUDE.md
!docs/
!.claude/
!.agents/